Introducing For You : With this version we are excited to roll out a transformative feature to enhance your Xumo experience: the new For You tab. This tab allows you to swipe through a curated selection of channels tailored just for you. With this new addition you ll find the For You option conveniently located in your bottom navigation streamlining your content discovery process. It s never been easier to find new content than it is with the For You tab. When you find something you re interested in simply turn your device into landscape mode and watch in full screen like you normally do. This build also includes bug fixes and performance improvements.

In this update we ve introduced a couple of enhancements designed to streamline your user experience. Firstly we ve relocated the Live Guide to the first position in the bottom tab navigation making it more accessible and intuitive for you. Secondly we ve added a mute button to the video player within the Discover section giving you control over the audio while you look for content in that section. In addition to these modifications we ve implemented a series of bug fixes and performance improvements.

We re excited to announce the latest update to Xumo Play! There are two highly requested features in this build: the Discover Tab and the Continue Watching Row. The Discover Tab is a curated experience that brings you the best content Xumo Play has to offer. With this new feature it s easier than ever to find something to watch on Xumo Play. You ll discover new shows movies and channels from across the Xumo Play platform. The Continue Watching Row provides you with a place in the app to resume watching your in progress content. You no longer have to go find the content you were watching we have moved it all into a row in the Discover Tab so that it s always in the same location and easy to find. We ve also included bug fixes and performance enhancements in this update.

We ve added Picture in Picture to make your viewing experience more enjoyable. Watch free movies and TV in more ways while multitasking on your device. Watching a movie and receive a text Or need to check email without interrupting your movie Now you easily can with Picture in Picture built right into the Xumo app. Your streaming experience continues on a thumbnail sized screen and can be positioned anywhere you d like while in Picture in Picture mode. You can even swipe it to the side when you need all the screen real estate you can get and swipe it back out anytime. You can even control the size of the thumbnail and pause your stream in the the Picture in Picture view. And of course this is all FREE. Free updates free movies free TV. Enjoy.
